Notes on extra features:


Implemented/Done:

Auto-mark project as in progress if a completed project's task is reopened via checkbox.

Add DELETE /api/projects/:id endpoint to allow deleting only completed projects.

Add delete project UI action in ProjectsPage with confirmation and restrict deletion to completed projects only.

Add toggle switch for dark theme.

Add delete project button next to edit in project details page with confirmation dialog.


Future Work:

If the last open task in a project is completed, mark the entire project as completed.

Allow editing in the projects list page (not only on the project details page).

Add loggers.

Allow users to add comments or notes to projects and tasks for better collaboration.

Enable selecting multiple tasks or projects for bulk completion, deletion, or status change.

Allow archiving completed projects instead of deleting (for historical reference).

Allow tasks to have subtasks for more granular tracking.